  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Dental Assistant",
  "description": "<p>✨ <strong>We’re Hiring: Dental Assistant</strong> ✨</p><h3>Key Responsibilities</h3><ul><li><p>Assist dentists during dental examinations, treatments, and procedures</p></li><li><p>Provide chairside support and ensure patient comfort throughout treatment</p></li><li><p>Prepare, clean, and sterilize dental instruments and equipment</p></li><li><p>Set up and turn over treatment rooms between patients</p></li><li><p>Maintain clinic cleanliness and adhere to infection control protocols</p></li><li><p>Support basic administrative or front desk duties when required</p></li></ul><h3>Requirements</h3><ul><li><p>Prior experience as a Dental Assistant is an advantage</p></li><li><p>Good communication and interpersonal skills</p></li><li><p>Positive attitude and strong team spirit</p></li><li><p>Able to multitask and work in a fast-paced clinical setting</p></li><li><p>Willing to learn and grow with the team</p></li></ul><h3>What We Offer</h3><ul><li><p>Competitive salary package (depends on experience)</p></li><li><p>On-the-job training and guidance provided</p></li><li><p>Flexible working schedule</p></li></ul><h3>Working Hours</h3><ul><li><p>Full time: 44 hours per week</p></li><li><p>5 working days (4 weekdays + 1 weekend day, rostered)<br /></p></li></ul><h3>Location</h3><p>📍 Clementi / West Coast area</p>",
