    "description": "<h2>One-Stop Dental Care</h2>\n<p>We believe that a confident smile starts with a nice set of teeth and achieving that should be hassle-free.</p>\n<p>To provide you with a <strong>one-stop dental service</strong>, Ocean Dental is a Clementi dental clinic well equipped with modern digital solutions in each of our treatment room.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Our team focus on building a family like environment for our staff.&nbsp;We currently have a positive and dynamic team of 20+ members and we are constantly open to recruiting more committed individuals to join our family.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Ocean Dental is built based on 4 Core Values:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Care without boundaries</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Quality at its best</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Integrity above all</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Long-lasting relationships</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>",
